---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms — Drureview" description="License terms for Drureview Core (Apache-2.0) and the paid one-time licenses.">
  <main class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/" class="back">← Drureview</a>
      <h1>Terms</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: June 11, 2026</p>

      <h2>The free Core</h2>
      <p>
        Drureview Core (the CLI review engine, the Claude Code skill, and the public fine-tuned
        models) is licensed under <strong>Apache License 2.0</strong>. The license text in the
        <a href="https://github.com/bartek-filipiuk/drureview-core" target="_blank" rel="noopener">repository</a>
        is authoritative. You can use it personally and commercially, forever, at no cost.
      </p>

      <h2>Paid licenses</h2>
      <p>
        Solo, Agency, and Site are <strong>one-time, perpetual licenses</strong> for the Pro layer
        (auto-fix, MCP server, web panel, PR-bot/CI, private-module indexing). Each purchase
        includes <strong>twelve months of updates</strong>; after that you keep every version you
        received and may optionally buy another year of updates. No subscription, no per-seat
        monthly billing. The full license agreement is delivered with your purchase and governs in
        case of any difference from this page.
      </p>

      <h2>What Drureview is — and isn't</h2>
      <p>
        Drureview is a <em>second</em> reviewer tuned for low false alarms. It is provided
        "as is", without warranty of any kind. It does not replace human code review, a security
        audit, or your own judgment, and we are not liable for issues a review did or did not
        flag. See the benchmark page for what we actually measured.
      </p>

      <h2>This site</h2>
      <p>
        Content on this site is informational. Prices shown before launch can change until your
        purchase completes; a reserved founding price is honored as promised in the reservation
        email. Drupal is a registered trademark of Dries Buytaert; Drureview is an independent
        project, not affiliated with or endorsed by the Drupal Association.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Bartek Filipiuk ·
        <a href="mailto:filipiuk.bartek@gmail.com">filipiuk.bartek@gmail.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <style>
    .legal-page { padding: 72px 0 96px; }
    .legal-page .container { max-width: 720px; }
    .legal-page .back {
      font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3); text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .legal-page .back:hover { color: var(--text-1); }
    .legal-page h1 { font-size: 34px; margin: 0 0 6px; }
    .legal-page .updated { color: var(--text-3); font-size: 13.5px; margin: 0 0 36px; }
    .legal-page h2 { font-size: 19px; margin: 32px 0 10px; }
    .legal-page p, .legal-page li { color: var(--text-2); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; }
    .legal-page code {
      font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 13px;
      background: var(--surface-2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .legal-page a { color: var(--accent-text); }
  </style>
</Layout>
